class daggit.core.operators.etl.DFMissingNum(replace)[source]¶

Bases: sklearn.base.TransformerMixin

Replaces missing values by input value or method.Below are the methods available. ‘mean’: replace missing values using the mean. ‘median’: replace missing values using the median ‘most_frequent’: replace missing values using the mode ‘backfill’ or ‘bfill’: use NEXT valid observation to fill gap. ‘pad’ or ‘ffill’: propagate last valid observation forward to next valid. Numeric value: Replaces with the input value Ex: repalce = “”mean”” for replacing with mean, replace = 0 for replacing with the numeric 0 Note: No quotes for numeric values
